txt.en: Supplies can be found at Zarkul-sulûn.\n\nYou should take inventory of supplies for Náin the Slakeless.
Náin the Slakeless can be found at Zarkul-sulûn.\n\nYou should report back to Náin the Slakeless.
Report back to Náin the Slakeless

'Bah, there is nothing but rushed preparations here! There needs to be order in war, or the enemy will find cracks and weaknesses. I do not even know what supplies we have available here at Zarkul-sulûn. I am tasking you with taking inventory. This is important, and I know that I can trust you.'
'I thank you for taking this detailed inventory. Our stores seem to be in better shape than I hoped. Indeed, we can work with this.'
Náin the Slakeless, Lord of the Iron Hills, has taken charge of Zarkul-sulûn with hopes to steer the dwarves to victory.
